
- Policy should have source IP address (-s/-d options in iptables)
- Commands to add and delete route entries (as a part of routing entries)


  ROUTE COMMANDS:
  -Commands to add and delete entries to the routing table (* these commands are not yet added, so we will require to add these)
  -Tabular repreesntation of the entries
  
  
